<div class="container text-center p-5">
<%#= HEADER SECTION  %>
  <div class="header pt-5 pb-5">
    <h1>Hi, I'm Poppy</h1>
    <h2>
      <span id="banner-typed-text"></span>
    </h2>
<%#= Font should be - font-family: 'Zilla Slab', serif; but this isn't getting picked up :(%>
  </div>

<%#= TOP SECTION CLASS  %>
<div class="top-section d-flex">
  <div class="left text-left">
    <div class="spacer mb-3">
      <h2>About me</h2>
    </div>
      <p>The desire to know how web apps are created, integrated and scaled led me to a coding bootcamp where I transitioned from digital marketer to full-stack web developer.</p>
      <p>Maintaining the skills of communication, coordination and prioritisation honed in my marketing career and combining them with my new found passion for adding flair to websites with JS/Stimulus, I keep the user experience at the forefront of my projects.</p>
      <p>I am keen to build my skills and learn more in order to help clients define and achieve their digital goals.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="right text-center">
    <div class="spacer mb-3">
      <h2>My stack</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="icons">
      <div class="first-row">
        <i class="fab fa-html5"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-css3-alt"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-js-square"></i>
      </div>
      
      <div class="second-row">
        <%= image_tag "ruby.svg", alt: "", width: 50 %>
        <%= image_tag "rails.svg", alt: "", width: 50 %>
        <%= image_tag "postgres.svg", alt: "", width: 50 %>
        <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="third-row">
        <i class="fab fa-bootstrap"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-sass"></i>    
        <%= image_tag "ui.svg", alt: "", width: 50 %>
        <%= image_tag "ux.svg", alt: "", width: 50 %>  
        <i class="fab fa-figma"></i>   
      </div>
      
      <div class="forth-row">
        <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-git-square"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-trello"></i>
        <i class="fab fa-slack"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%#= CAROUSEL  %>

<div class="spacer m-5">
  <h2>My projects</h2>
</div>

<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2" class="active"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/03/15/13/27/rough-horn-2146181_1280.jpg" alt="First slide">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h3>Hubbly</h3>
          <h4><a href="http://www.hubbly.online/">Hubbly.online</a></h4>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum volutpat interdum arcu, vel porttitor urna pharetra eu. Integer suscipit fringilla lectus. Orci varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Duis tempus ex ac lorem iaculis, non eleifend turpis porttitor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/03/09/09/43/person-1245959_1280.jpg" alt="Second slide">
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/04/23/22/01/mountains-736886_1280.jpg" alt="Third slide">
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
